# 懵然不知
(pos:形容詞)
<explanation>
yue:形容人對某件事完全不知情，毫無覺察，好似睇唔到或聽唔到。
eng:describes someone who is completely unaware of something, having no clue or perception of it.
<eg>
yue:佢對呢件事懵然不知，直至有人指出佢錯咗。 (keoi5 deoi3 ni1 gin6 si6 mong5 jin4 bat1 zi1, zi6 si3 jau5 jan4 zi2 gun2 keoi5 co3 zo2.)
eng:He was completely unaware of this matter until someone pointed out his mistake. [end of text]


